{"id":6736,"date":"2023-10-25T03:53:00","date_gmt":"2023-10-25T03:53:00","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/?p=6736"},"modified":"2023-11-22T03:55:07","modified_gmt":"2023-11-22T03:55:07","slug":"king-mongkuts-university-of-technology-thonbury-thailand-kunjungi-smansa","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/2023\/10\/25\/king-mongkuts-university-of-technology-thonbury-thailand-kunjungi-smansa\/","title":{"rendered":"King Mongkuts University of Technology Thonbury Thailand Kunjungi SMANSA"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>SMANSA di Mata Negera Asean: Salah Satu Sekolah Terbaik Di Asean.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>King Mongkuts University of Technology Thonbury Thailand beekunjung untuk mensosialsasikan kampus di Thailand bahwasanya thailand termasuk negara dengan pendidikan terbaik di Negeranya serta diakui di Dunia. Dalam hal ini bermaksud mengajak pelajar Indonesia khususnya pelajar SMAN 1 Bandung untuk melanjutkan pendidikan disana. &#8220;karena kami mengenal SMAN 1 Bandung salah satu sekolah terbaik&#8221; ujarnua dalam bahasa thailand &#8220;SMAN 1 Bandung \u0e40\u0e1b\u0e47\u0e19\u0e2b\u0e19\u0e36\u0e48\u0e07\u0e43\u0e19\u0e42\u0e23\u0e07\u0e40\u0e23\u0e35\u0e22\u0e19\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48\u0e14\u0e35\u0e17\u0e35\u0e48\u0e2a\u0e38\u0e14&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/smansabandung_1700625236446-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"6737\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/smansabandung_1700625236446.jpeg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/?attachment_id=6737#main\" class=\"wp-image-6737\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/smansabandung_1700625236446-800x800.jpeg 800w, https:\/\/sman1bdg.sch.id\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/11\/smansaband